# React Native Architecture

Policy: `.ai/policies/frontend-react-native.md`

## State

- Redux Toolkit only for application state
- No `useState`, `useReducer`, custom `Context` for app/page/form/workflow/loading/error/selection
- `useAppDispatch`, `useAppSelector`, memoized selectors
- Pure reducers — no I/O, timers, navigation, or network in reducers

## API

- RTK Query only — single `baseApi`, typed endpoints, tags, invalidation
- No `fetch`, Axios, or direct HTTP from UI/hooks/screens/slices

## UI Structure

```
src/app/ | shared/ui/{atoms,molecules,organisms,templates}/ | entities/ | features/ | widgets/ | pages/
```

Business logic in features/entities — not in atoms/molecules/templates.

## Side Effects

RTK Query lifecycle, listener middleware, or named async workflows with cleanup.

## Lint Targets (when configured)

Error on: `useState`, `useReducer`, `createContext`, `useContext`, `fetch`, `axios` — ADR exceptions only.

## Tooling (Enforced)

```bash
npm run lint           # ESLint + eslint-plugin-jsdoc
npm run format:check   # Prettier
```

JSDoc required on all exports (Documenter Agent). Policy: `.ai/policies/frontend-tooling.md`.

## Real-Time Feed

Product requires live transaction updates without manual refresh — WebSocket/SSE + RTK integration (ADR required).
